OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fmostly cloudy this evening and
OL,7,Fovernight with some clearer spells,
OL,8,Fthese mostly across the north. Dry for
OL,9,Fmany but some outbreaks of rain still
OL,10,Fpossible, especially in the west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FLargely dry start with bright
OL,13,Fspells in the north and east. Through
OL,14,Fthe morning, cloud and rain will
OL,15,Fspread east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
