OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy and breezy few days with spells
OL,7,Fof rain spreading eastwards. Rain may
OL,8,Fbe heavy and persistent in the west
OL,9,Fwith the best of any brighter spells
OL,10,Fin east.
